          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Forum 3: GenAI Architecture Council (Quarterly)"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Purpose and Scope"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The architecture council is a quarterly 2-hour session where cross-team architectural decisions are made. It has authority that the other forums do not: it can mandate architectural standards across teams, approve or reject proposals to adopt new platform components, and initiate deprecation of shared infrastructure."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Membership and Authority"
          }
        ]
      },
