                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " Proposals to add a new model provider, vector database, or orchestration framework to the approved platform component list are reviewed here. Adoption requires a proof-of-concept from at least one product team."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
