            "text": "Council ADR Template"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "codeBlock",
        "attrs": {
          "language": "markdown"
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "# Cross-Team ADR: [Title]\n\n## Status\nProposed | Accepted | Rejected | Superseded\n\n## Context\n[Why this decision is needed, and why it requires council review rather than\nbeing made within a single team]\n\n## Teams Affected\n- Team A: [how they are affected]\n- Team B: [how they are affected]\n\n## Decision\n[The specific architectural decision]\n\n## Rationale\n[Why this option was chosen over alternatives]\n\n## Migration Requirements\n- Team A: [specific changes required, estimated effort, deadline]\n- Team B: [specific changes required, estimated effort, deadline]\n\n## Fitness Function Impact\n[Which fitness functions need updating across teams, and who owns those updates]\n\n## Reversal Criteria\n[Conditions under which this decision would be revisited by the council]\n\n## Vote Record\n| Member | Vote | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| Platform lead | Approve | |\n| Team A tech lead | Approve | |\n| Team B tech lead | Abstain | Not yet affected |\n| Security rep | Approve | No new compliance scope |\n"
          }
        ]
