            "text": "## Experiment Result — [SHORT TITLE]\n\n**Team:** Team A  \n**Date:** 2025-07-01  \n**Forum tag:** #prompt-guild candidate\n\n**Hypothesis:** Reducing system prompt length by 30% will not degrade\neval score but will reduce token cost.\n\n**What we ran:**\n- Baseline: 850-token system prompt, eval set n=400\n- Treatment: 590-token system prompt (trimmed redundant instructions)\n- Metric: exact-match score + cost-per-call\n\n**Result:**\n- Eval score: 0.812 → 0.808 (-0.5% — within acceptable range)\n- Cost per call: -18% (significant)\n\n**Conclusion:** Confirmed. Shorter prompt achieves same quality at lower cost.\nRecommend all teams audit system prompts for redundant instructions.\n\n**Next step:** Submitting to prompt pattern library at next guild session.\n"
